Have a look a the beginning of `faxview.tcl' and choose your defaults.
Don't forget to insert the correct path to wish(1) in the first line.
Then say

    $ install -m 755 faxview.tcl <somewhere>/bin/faxview
    $ install -m 444 faxview.man <somewhere>/man/man1/faxview.1


